<p>June 18th.<br/>Trinity- Sunday- Mass 5.30 a.m. (6.30 a.m. by watch)   Artillery silent at Ypres- 2 Taubes brought down at   <strike>Ypres</strike>   Armentieres   Departure for A.D.S.<br/>June. 19th.<br/>Day. Duty in D.R.<br/>June 20th<br/>Huns shell Armentieres- Destruction of Church &amp; dwellings- Death of Von Molthe- Few Cases.<br/>June 21st.<br/>Longest day- (daylight 10 p. m &amp; 2.30 a. m) - I meet a couple of the H. H. Boys.</p>
